des:
Link Twenty Six Miler (26Miler) with your strava account and check your activities just using your voice.
A strava.com account is required to be able to use this skill. As of now, voice spoken in English language is supported.

Twenty Six Miler (26Miler) is not sponsored or endorsed by strava.com.
